Class AbstractDevice

java.lang.Object
AbstractDevice
All Implemented Interfaces:
Device
Direct Known Subclasses:
Headphone, Keyboard, Laptop, Smartphone, TV
public abstract class AbstractDevice extends Object implements Device
Represents a generic device in the inventory system. This abstract class provides common implementation for devices.

  • Constructor Details

    • AbstractDevice

      public AbstractDevice(String name, String categoryName, double price, int quantity)
      Constructs an AbstractDevice with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the device.
      categoryName - the category name of the device.
      price - the price of the device.
      quantity - the quantity of the device in inventory. Since all these operations are executed sequentially and each of them has a constant time complexity, Time Complexity is O(1)
